title: DFR035 - District Facility Radio - Hardom Mix
description:
Techno music movement on behalf of the District Facility who presents once in a month radio cast. Global and local techno scene news, exclusive tracks, dating with new names.

----------------------------------

Guest: Hardom born in Italy 24 years ago... From an early age he had a love for music and began playing music at age 12.
Arises from techno darker, harder and here comes the name Hardom.

He performs in the old school or new school, it is irrelevant because it does not do it for fame or for fashion, but for passion!

Life is just techno!

Support by Darpa, 2Loud, Lorenzo D'Ianni, Manuel Pisu, Angy Kore, Silvano Scarpetta, Roman Kramer, Albert Kraner, Electrorites, Loso and more...
